            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                [<expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ar</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">Commodus</del> Antoninus A]u<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan></supplied> Pius <expan><abbr>Sarm</abbr><ex>aticus</ex></expan> Ger<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>anicus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imus</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>annicus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>orti</ex></expan></supplied> I <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elia</ex></expan> Antonina&amp;lt;e&amp;gt; |(miliariae) <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Hem</abbr><ex>esenorum</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>fecit curam agente <del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Cornelio Felice Plo</supplied>tiano le[<expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan></del>]
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung als Deckplatte für ein spätantikes Grab. Das Erhaltene ist in mehrere Teile gebrochen. Rekonstruierte Breite: circa 5 m. Mehrere heute fehlende Buchstaben waren bei der Auffindung noch vorhanden: G in [A]u[g.] und M in Ger[m.] (Z. 1), H in [Hem.] (Z. 2), [[GPR]] in [[[leg. pr.]]] (Z. 3). Sehr viele Ligaturen; teilweise Buchstaben klein in andere Buchstaben eingefügt. Lesung und Ergänzung nach Mráv. (B): RIU: Z. 3: nicht gelesen.</p>
            </div>
